snakegame

Class Sprite

  • java.lang.Object
    • snakegame.Sprite

  • public class Sprite
extends java.lang.Object
    Sprite.java is a utility class to help manage the creation of elements in the Snake game. Apple.java, Snake.java, and Wall.java should all extend this class and leverage the functions in it. You may modify this class but please do not make any object-specific modifications; whatever you change in this class needs to work for all objects that use this class.
